<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Source Build</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .features li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #555;
        }
        .features li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .features li:before {
            content: "✓ ";
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Source Build!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>!</h2>
            
            <p>
                We're thrilled to have you join our growing community of buyers, sellers, and drivers at Source Build - your premier e-commerce marketplace.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Your account has been successfully created and verified. You're now ready to explore everything Source Build has to offer!
            </p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <h3>What you can do now:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Browse thousands of products from verified sellers</li>
                    <li>Enjoy secure payment options and buyer protection</li>
                    <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
                    <li>Connect with sellers through our chat feature</li>
                    <li>Leave reviews and help build our community</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta-button">Go to Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                <strong>Need help getting started?</strong><br>
                <p>Please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@sourcebuild.com">support@sourcebuild.com</a></p>
            </p>
            
         
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                This email was sent to <%= email %><br>
                You received this email because you recently created an account at Source Build.
            </p>
            
     
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                © <%= year %> Source Build. All rights reserved.<br>
                <a href="<%= privacyUrl %>">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="<%= termsUrl %>">Terms of Service</a> | 
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>